Package: theeconomist
Type: Package
Title: The Economist article text analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marco Del Treppo
Maintainer: Marco Del Treppo <marco.deltreppo@studenti.unimi.it>
Description: Scrap article text from The Economist website (https://www.economist.com/).
             Build a tibble with the most frequent words. 
             Plot the most frequent words with ggplot.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    rvest,
    tibble,
    tidytext,
    ggplot2,
    xml2,
    magrittr
